Description
You will be responsible for the efficient running of the department in line with Hyatt International's Corporate Strategies and brand standards, whilst meeting employee, guest and owner expectations. The Assistant Pastry Chef is responsible to ensure the smooth and efficient running of the Pastry Department,  assisting the Pastry Chef with the implementation of Hyatt's People Philosophy
throughout the hotel and contribute to the overall success of outlets and banquets, in accordance with the hotel’s standards and financial goals.
Qualifications
Ideally with an apprenticeship or professional diploma in Food Production with pastry specialisation. Minimum 2 years work experience as or Assistant Pastry Chef in larger operation. Good practical, operational and adequate administrative skills with a flair for creativity are a must.
